1. Danas sam dobro *raspoložen*. (Today I am in a good mood.)
2. Koliko si već dugo u ovakvom *raspoloženju*? (How long have you been in this mood?)
3. Njeno *raspoloženje* se promenilo kada je videla poklon. (Her mood changed when she saw the gift.)
4. Hoću da se *raspoložim* uz dobru knjigu. (I want to get in a good mood by reading a good book.)
5. *Raspoložen* sam za izlazak večeras. (I am in the mood for going out tonight.)
6. Učiniću sve što mogu da *raspoložim* goste na zabavi. (I will do everything I can to put the guests in a good mood at the party.)
7. Njegov šarm je uspeo da *raspoloži* i najozbiljnije goste. (His charm managed to put even the most serious guests in a good mood.)
8. *Raspoloženje* u sobi se odjednom promenilo kada su se pojavili nepozvani gosti. (The mood in the room suddenly changed when uninvited guests appeared.)
9. Ne volim kada mi neko kvari *raspoloženje*. (I don't like it when someone ruins my mood.)
10. Njegov humor je uvek uspevao da *raspoloži* druge ljude. (His humor always managed to put other people in a good mood.)